snippet.title: VISEGUNNE - OFFICIAL TRAILER - WISHLIST NOW
snippet.description:
WISHLIST NOW ON STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2882040/VISEGUNNE/

VISEGUNNE is a single-player shoot 'em up featuring explosive, narrative-driven missions, a vast arsenal of weapons, and over-the-top visual effects. Set in an era where the human soul is harnessed as a power source, join the DIVINITY SPACE DEFENSE CORPORATION's elite mercenaries to confront pro-Earth terrorists threatening the fragile peace of space. Shoot. Survive. Ascend.

Follow Us:
